<pb n="0043b" xml:id="I01.0016.0043b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0043b01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0043b0101" cb:type="pre">熙平二年太歲在丁酉三月<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">丙</unclear>酉朔□日壬戌
<lb ed="I" n="0043b02"/>　比丘劉僧<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">真</unclear>少□道門。志□於外。□□□累
<lb ed="I" n="0043b03"/>　<note n="0043001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">刼＝劫【史】</note><note n="0043001" resp="ihp" type="mod">刼【佛拓】，劫【史】</note><app n="0043001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">刼</rdg></app>之苦。□□有在□□緣以□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0043b04"/>　臨高照之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">隆</unclear>□。並四時□□□□□樂逾□
<lb ed="I" n="0043b05"/>天宮。供施精巖。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">使</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">外</unclear>□万路歸□。道俗恭□連
<lb ed="I" n="0043b06"/>車蓋疋興逮。上為皇帝延綿。師僧先<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">妣</unclear>。造石像
<lb ed="I" n="0043b07"/>一<note n="0043002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">駈＝軀【史】</note><note n="0043002" resp="ihp" type="mod">駈【佛拓】，軀【史】</note><app n="0043002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軀</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">駈</rdg></app>。興福以誌。願皇帝隆綿。師僧父母。朗朗與
<lb ed="I" n="0043b08"/>三光並暈。覆則与乾<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">晨</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">同</unclear>□。下為四部道俗欽
<lb ed="I" n="0043b09"/>明。核業藏潤。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">宿</unclear>信<note n="0043003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢏏＝彌【史】</note><note n="0043003" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢏏【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0043003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𢏏</rdg></app>樂。敬崇三寶。□智龍天。任
<lb ed="I" n="0043b10"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">顥</unclear>皇朝有類氏人女□□□外渡四碍。除充主
<lb ed="I" n="0043b11"/>公<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">郡</unclear>想。競業疇延。室家和望。眾陳天<note n="0043004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">笇＝算【史】</note><note n="0043004" resp="ihp" type="mod">笇【佛拓】，算【史】</note><app n="0043004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">算</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">笇</rdg></app>正始<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">智</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0043b12"/>然合邑子等。閻石記<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">念</unclear>。永世留名。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">為</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">恐</unclear>事記願
<lb ed="I" n="0043b13"/>登覽首。未<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">來</unclear>世中。彌勒三會。□等蓋□。願願從
<lb ed="I" n="0043b14"/>心。三有群生。普同成佛。</p></cb:div><cb:div>
